org.eclipse.viatra.query.patternlanguage.emf.scoping

Interface IMetamodelProviderInstance

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IMetamodelProvider
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GenModelMetamodelProviderService, MetamodelProviderService, ResourceSetMetamodelProviderService, TargetPlatformMetamodelProviderService

    public interface IMetamodelProviderInstance
extends IMetamodelProvider
    A single metamodel provider instance, used by the CompoundMetamodelProviderService to delegate the selection of metamodels. The interface extends IMetamodelProvider by priority and name definition.
    Since:
    1.0
